I just wanted to check that you have all of the login credentials you need now for each of the systems?

 

I’ve found out a couple of things during conversations with LearnUpon that you’ll need to be aware of, these aren’t changes to the spec but just details of how their system handles new account registrations –

 

-          To provide LearnUpon login credentials to the candidates we’ll need to use the GroupInviteCourseEnrollment call in the API which will trigger an email to the email address supplied for the candidate, they then click a link in the email and are instructed to choose a password. This then confirms their account and enrols them on the relevant course(s).

-          If multiple courses are booked in Shopify for the same candidate then only one call needs to go through the API with the candidates details linked to multiple courses so that only one account is created for them in LearnUpon.

 

If you need any clarification please get in touch.
